and maybe supporting

00:49:14.650 --> 00:49:17.900
the theory of the
Big Bang, or is it

00:49:17.900 --> 00:49:21.570
really more like stuff
that's 4.6 million years old

00:49:21.570 --> 00:49:23.381
and is very localized dust?

00:49:23.381 --> 00:49:25.130
NATALIE STARKEY: So
