00:50:52.400 --> 00:50:54.170
get caught into the
gravity of our sun.

00:50:54.170 --> 00:50:55.390
It just zipped by.

00:50:55.390 --> 00:50:57.470
And it came from some
other star system.

00:50:57.470 --> 00:50:58.680
We have idea where.

00:50:58.680 --> 00:51:02.550
And it's probably been some like
interstellar travel forever.

00:51:02.550 --> 00:51:04.020
Who knows when it formed?

00:51:04.020 --> 00:51:05.980
It came from very far away.

00:51:05.980 --> 00:51:08.700
So it's been going for at
least billions of years.

00:51:08.700 --> 00:51:10.457
And it just zipped through.

00:51:10.457 --> 00:51:11.790
So we don't know a lot about it.

00:51:11.790 --> 00:51:12.840
We just know that it's--

00:51:12.840 --> 00:51:14.640
I think called Mu--

00:51:14.640 --> 00:51:15.480
is it called Mu-ama?

00:51:15.480 --> 00:51:16.857
