Just one.

00:52:40.570 --> 00:52:44.740
NATALIE STARKEY: So I would want
to go and explore the Kuiper

00:52:44.740 --> 00:52:46.376
Belt better, get samples of it.

00:52:46.376 --> 00:52:48.000
I'd want to explore
more of the comets.

